flowchart LR
    subgraph Clients[客户端]
        GP[gRPC Producer]
        GS[SimpleConsumer]
        GPC[gRPC PushConsumer]
        RC[经典 Remoting Client]
    end

    GP --> EP[Endpoint / VIP / LoadBalancer]
    GS --> EP
    GPC --> EP

    EP --> PX1[Proxy 1]
    EP --> PX2[Proxy 2]

    PX1 --> NS[NameServer]
    PX2 --> NS
    PX1 --> B1[Broker]
    PX2 --> B2[Broker]

    RC --> NS
    RC --> B1
    RC --> B2

    B1 <-->|复制| B1S[Broker Replica]
    B2 <-->|复制| B2S[Broker Replica]

    CT[Controller Raft Group] -.选主与副本元数据.-> B1
    CT -.选主与副本元数据.-> B2
